continue means skip button and break means exit button
continue:

fruits = ["apple", "banana", "cherry", "date"]
for x in fruits:
    if x == "banana":
        continue
    print(x)

output: 
apple
cherry
date

break:

fruits = ["apple", "banana", "cherry", "date"]

for x in fruits:
    if x == "banana":
        break
    print(x)

Output: 
apple
